title: La Ville du Port Spatial
info:
After roaming several desperate months in the domains of low technology, the protagonist finally reaches a shining city where one can see huge cargo crafts landing and departing

--

-tool: Schism Tracker

-The song was sent to Sundown 2014 tracked music compo but it sounded totally distorted on the stream for some reason, so I asked them to discard it
